title: Capture Medusa's Head
summary: Medusa was once a priestess of Athena. Poseidon took a fancy on her to get back at Athena and brought her to the local temple for Athena. Athena was furius that they were getting romantic at the foot of her statue, cursing Medusa. She turned her hair into serpants and made it so any mortal who would look upon her gaze into stone.

title: Weave baskets with the water nymphs
summary: Summer is fast approaching and our fundraiser is coming up in preparation for a big quest forseen by the Oracle. Participate in working with the water nymphs to weave baskets.
